{
    "info": {
        "_postman_id": "eicher-app-v2-2026",
        "name": "đźš› Eicher Driver App",
        "description": "Complete API collection for the Eicher (main truck) Driver mobile app.\n\n**Role required:** `driver eicher`\n\n**E2E Flow:**\n1. Login â†’ capture token\n2. Check Today Log â†’ decide whether to show Start Shift screen\n3. POST Start Shift (once per day)\n4. GET Dashboard â†’ note your {{assignmentId}}\n5. POST Submit Trip Report\n6. PATCH End Shift (once per day)\n\n**Assignment Status Flow:**\n`PENDING` â†’ `COMPLETED` (set by Munshi packing report) â†’ `APPROVED` (set by OM)",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
    "variable": [
        {
            "key": "baseUrl",
            "value": "http://localhost:5000",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "token",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        },
        {
            "key": "assignmentId",
            "value": "",
            "type": "string"
        }
    ],
    "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
            {
                "key": "token",
                "value": "{{token}}",
                "type": "string"
            }
        ]
    },
    "item": [
        {
            "name": "0. Auth",
            "item": [
                {
                    "name": "POST Login",
                    "event": [
                        {
                            "listen": "test",
                            "script": {
                                "exec": [
                                    "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                                    "  var data = pm.response.json();",
                                    "  if (data && data.token) {",
                                    "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', data.token);",
                                    "    console.log('âś… Eicher token saved:', data.token);",
                                    "  }",
                                    "}"
                                ],
                                "type": "text/javascript"
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "request": {
                        "auth": {
                            "type": "noauth"
                        },
                        "method": "POST",
                        "header": [
                            {
                                "key": "Content-Type",
                                "value": "application/json"
                            }
                        ],
                        "body": {
                            "mode": "raw",
                            "raw": "{\n  \"mobileNo\": \"1000000000\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}",
                            "options": {
                                "raw": {
                                    "language": "json"
                                }
                            }
                        },
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/login",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "users",
                                "login"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Login as Eicher Driver. The test script auto-saves the JWT to `{{token}}`.\n\n**Response fields of interest:**\n- `token` â€” JWT bearer token\n- `user.role` â€” should be `driver eicher`\n- `user.vehicleId` â€” the pre-assigned vehicle"
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
                {
                    "name": "GET My Profile",
                    "request": {
                        "method": "GET",
                        "header": [],
                        "url": {
                            "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/driver/profile",
                            "host": [
                                "{{baseUrl}}"
                            ],
                            "path": [
                                "api",
                                "driver",
                                "profile"
                            ]
                        },
                        "description": "Returns full driver profile including populated vehicleId (vehicleNumber, vehicleType). Use this to pre-fill the Start Shift form with the default vehicle number."
                    },
                    "response": []
                },
